Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:49.17,Main,,0,0,0,,And so, having completed their Promise Kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:54.60,Main,,0,0,0,,the two began a journey beyond severance,\Nguided by the star of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:59.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mom, what's your new story about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:04.81,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the story of you and the girl\Nwho taught us about Kumaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:06.82,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the last page.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.82,0:01:10.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh... What girl is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.61,0:01:14.24,Main,,0,0,0,,You know her! The girl you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:18.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You told me you sang\Nthe "love" song together, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:21.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know any girl like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:22.25,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:28.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha... don't tell me... you've forgotten her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.93,0:01:42.02,Main,,0,0,0,,We hated you from the beginning--\Nand loved you from the beginning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:47.90,Main,,0,0,0,,And so we wanted to become true\Nfriends with you. To cross the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:55.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikumaaaaaaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:01:56.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:02:03.54,Main,,0,0,0,,"THE GIRL THAT I FORGOT"\N{\i1}Viens avec moi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:06.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Church chimes echo in the distance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:09.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Offer up a prayer and betray today{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:15.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wander in a dark forest, then become{\i0}\N{\i1}the morning moon at the Wall of Severance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:17.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't join the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:21.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once I've made you stickier{\i0}\N{\i1}with sweet, thin honey{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:25.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, approve me, I'll be a good girl{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:31.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Picture-book pages dancing on{\i0}\N{\i1}the breeze shake up shadowy memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:37.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:43.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be waiting you-know-where,{\i0}\N{\i1}in an empty world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.79,0:02:48.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if everything falls apart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:55.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you have to gracefully writhe,{\i0}\N{\i1}even if you have to bend space-time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:58.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Find me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:10.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flower petals will slowly{\i0}\N{\i1}enfold us on a starry night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:11.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:14.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:17.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:26.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}J'ai besoin de toi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:46.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish you could've seen\Nthe look on Kureha Tsubaki's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:48.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't know such pleasure existed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:53.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I love you. You found me from among the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:59.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not a weak girl at the mercy\Nof the Invisible Storm anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:03.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Now I'm someone important,\Nwho won't be excluded. Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:06.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Bear shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:21.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Simmer, porridge, simmer softly!\NGrowl, growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:26.22,Main,,0,0,0,,After that, we got official permission\Nto freeload at Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}'s!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:29.52,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, we're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:33.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko's just a step away\Nfrom getting her Promise Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.07,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:48.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't back down on love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:57.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurishiro, why did you\Nprotect Sumika's letter for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Why, when it cost you so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:09.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurishiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:11.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Good, I'm glad you're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:18.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:21.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:22.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:29.25,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as you don't forget love,\Nyou'll never be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:31.12,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't give up on love,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:34.08,Main,,0,0,0,,even if you lose something,\Nyou'll never be invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:36.38,Main,,0,0,0,,How do you know those words?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:40.46,Main,,0,0,0,,You are my Lady Kumaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:44.80,Main,,0,0,0,,"Lady Kumaria"... from the picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:06:00.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicious smell. You smell, Kureha. Growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:04.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Search for what you hope for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:07.07,Main,,0,0,0,,What I hope for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:08.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:13.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Search for what? Search for it where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:18.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I know you remember--\Nit's in your fingers, in your lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:22.26,Main,,0,0,0,,In you right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:25.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, give me the Promise Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:29.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Promise... Kiss? From me to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:34.52,Main,,0,0,0,,And me to you. Then everything\Nwill awaken, and everything will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Did I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:54.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no--what a thing to dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:57.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! The honey porridge is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:07.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}, what's wrong? You're blushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:15.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I-It's your imagination! Now watch\NYurishiro, okay? She's really sweating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:17.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:20.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Lady Kumaria...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:31.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would I dream that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:35.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, did you have fun\Nwith your friend again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:40.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep! I taught her the love song today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:42.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:48.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh! She's my special friend,\Nso she gets an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:52.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I see! You really love her, don't you, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:54.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:58.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.23,0:08:02.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Who is "her"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:05.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I notice before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:08.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}did {\i0}have a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:15.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom, tell me... who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:24.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I hear there was another bear attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:26.76,Main,,0,0,0,,No way! Wasn't it exterminated?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:29.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Remember, that student what's-her-name shot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:33.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! The one who brings\Nher friends bad luck, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:37.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, another girl\Nfrom her class got attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:38.77,Main,,0,0,0,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:40.06,Main,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:43.06,Main,,0,0,0,,So, who was it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:45.40,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Harishima?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:53.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. She was discovered\Nthis morning in front of the flowerbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:57.66,Main,,0,0,0,,They declared it a bear attack\Nbased on her wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:00.37,Main,,0,0,0,,But wait, I shot the bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:04.63,Main,,0,0,0,,This means there's another bear\Nstill lurking in the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:08.72,Main,,0,0,0,,It's horrifying.\NThe bears took not only Reia's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:14.01,Main,,0,0,0,,but even the proof of\Nour love: that star pendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yuriika?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:21.48,Main,,0,0,0,,The bear with Reia's pendant--\Nthat's our mortal enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:25.90,Main,,0,0,0,,One day we'll find it, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:28.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:33.74,Main,,0,0,0,,So, what was it you wanted to ask me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:37.62,Main,,0,0,0,,My... old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Old friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:43.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. I remembered while I was\Nlistening to Mom's music box.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,When I was little, I had a special friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,We called her "her."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:54.51,Main,,0,0,0,,But for some reason,\NI can't remember her face or her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:57.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought you might know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:03.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\NReia did say something strange--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:06.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Shortly before she died, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:12.03,Main,,0,0,0,,She said you'd suddenly forgotten your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:17.91,Main,,0,0,0,,What else... Ah yes, that book,\N{\i1}The Moon Girl and the Forest Girl{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:22.58,Main,,0,0,0,,She said it was about you and your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:26.84,Main,,0,0,0,,A story about me and "her"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:29.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:34.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Grow-sniffle... Your fever won't come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:36.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:45.02,Main,,0,0,0,,This'll turn you into a nice,\Ncold growl-sicle, and you'll feel better!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:46.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:54.90,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:58.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Kumaria is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:01.66,Main,,0,0,0,,She is the world's mother,\Nthe one who approves all living things
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:03.58,Main,,0,0,0,,and gives them love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:13.92,Main,,0,0,0,,The cub who appeared the day\Nof that silvery blizzard was named "Ginko."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:16.47,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Several Years Later・(History)"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.93,0:11:20.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:21.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:24.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You're an unwanted bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.02,0:11:27.35,Main,,0,0,0,,A lonely lone wolfsbane nobody will ever find!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:33.07,Main,,0,0,0,,What's {\i1}this{\i0}? You think you're\Nthe Lone Wolfsbane king or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Lone Wolfsbane.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:38.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Lone Wolfsbane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:40.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Lone Wolfsbane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Bear shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:46.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut {\i1}up{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:50.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Thus Ginko was left all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:54.55,Main,,0,0,0,,And at some point, she became\Nknown as "Ginko the Lone Wolfsbane."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:55.55,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Ginko the Lone Wolfsbane・(Bear)"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:12:00.64,MainTop,,0,0,0,,I see now. This world is ruled by power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:03.64,Main,,0,0,0,,No one is kind to the weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:06.73,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a dog-eat-dog, bear-eat-salmon world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Kumami! Dinnertime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:09.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:11.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:14.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Kumako! Come back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:14.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:16.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Kumary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:17.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:18.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Kumargaret!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:19.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:20.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Kumacaron!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:21.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:26.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Kumacaron, today's your favorite--salmon pizza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:28.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I love salmon pizza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:32.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:38.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Eventually, the Day of Severance came.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:49.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Bear cubs in Ginko's situation were\Ngathered by the superior Lady Kumaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:55.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Rejoice, for you have been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:13:00.53,MainTop,,0,0,0,,For surely you were unwanted bears,\Nbut now you shall be given a chance at approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,In this world, only One\Nneeds you and gives you approval:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Lady Kumaria!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:14.42,Main,,0,0,0,,"Lady Kumaria"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:18.88,Main,,0,0,0,,From this day forth, you are cubs of Kumaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:23.39,Main,,0,0,0,,You shall be guard-bears of the\Nboundary between bears and humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:32.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Exclude the vermin called "humans"\Nfrom our border and protect our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:38.32,Main,,0,0,0,,That is the mission you shall carry out\Nfor the holy mother Kumaria!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:44.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:45.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:48.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:52.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Human excluded, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:57.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Humans excluded, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:04.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:08.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Humans excluded, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:12.81,Main,,0,0,0,,HQ! HQ! Request backup immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:20.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:23.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Bears excluded!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:24.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:32.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko believed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:36.25,Main,,0,0,0,,If she fulfilled her mission,\Nsurely Kumaria would approve her,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:40.17,Main,,0,0,0,,and she would one day be granted love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:43.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not an unwanted Lone Wolfsbane!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:47.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll eat lots more people, and get approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:51.10,Main,,0,0,0,,And then someday, Lady Kumaria...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.61,Main,,0,0,0,,...will grant me love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:21.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Day after day, the moon girl\Nand the forest girl gazed at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:25.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Is the forest girl "her," then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:27.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:28.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:31.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}, you're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:33.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:34.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:37.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:40.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! What book is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:42.52,Main,,0,0,0,,A picture book my mom wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:45.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Really? Can I read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:48.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, but I'll warn you:\Nit doesn't have an ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:50.24,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:53.45,Main,,0,0,0,,My mom died before she finished it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:55.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:57.29,Main,,0,0,0,,She was killed by a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:01.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go check on Yurishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:13.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurishiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:15.85,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:20.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko loves you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.15,0:16:24.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Why? We only just met, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:27.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I haven't done anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:32.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Your wounds and your pain\Nshould have been mine, but you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.47,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.61,Main,,0,0,0,,She's done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:09.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she'd slow us down. Let's exclude her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:12.07,Main,,0,0,0,,--Exclude her.\N--Exclude her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:13.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Exclude her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:17.08,Main,,0,0,0,,--Exclude her.\N--The animal world is merciless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:20.87,Main,,0,0,0,,The weak, those who can't do\Nthe same things as the group,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:23.04,Main,,0,0,0,,are summarily excluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:27.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh... I guess I failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:31.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You're an unwanted bear. A Lone Wolfsbane!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:33.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Lone Wolfsbane...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:41.52,Main,,0,0,0,,So I don't get to be found, then.\NI don't get to be approved by anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:46.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to die here, without ever having love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:55.12,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the love song my mom taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:18:00.29,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay, you're not alone. I'm your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:04.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:09.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Lady... Kumaria...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:20.39,Main,,0,0,0,,"Lady Kumaria"...?\NWhy do you know that storybook?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:21.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:33.40,Main,,0,0,0,,G-Good, I'm glad you're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:35.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, that song you just--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:40.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, um... I'll go tell Yurigasaki that you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:49.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Tee-hee, it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:53.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! Ginger milk complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:59.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Now I just need to mix in lots of honey,\Nand I'll have honey ginger milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:06.02,Main,,0,0,0,,There, all done. You two enjoy it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:10.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:16.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You two really love\Nhoney ginger milk, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:20.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's the flavor of our love!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:26.58,Main,,0,0,0,,What's up? You spaced out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:30.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I remembered something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:38.39,Main,,0,0,0,,A friend and I drank Mom's\Nhoney ginger milk here, a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:46.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Until just now, I'd forgotten how that felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:49.52,Main,,0,0,0,,But I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:55.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Honey ginger milk is Ginko's love flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:20:00.12,Main,,0,0,0,,The flavor that tells her\Nshe's not all alone in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:03.20,Main,,0,0,0,,The taste of a twinkling star.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:06.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurishiro's love flavor...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:11.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! But I haven't added\Nthe honey to finish it off yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:20.72,Main,,0,0,0,,How could I forget a friend\NI cared about so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:21.26,Main,,0,0,0,,"The Moon Girl and the Forest Girl"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:26.23,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, I loved her so much, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:28.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Muahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:32.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Honey ginger milk will get Ginko\Nand Kure-{\i1}chin {\i0}totally close in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:35.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I am {\i1}so {\i0}clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:42.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}'s mom's book?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:44.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Moon Girl and the Forest Girl{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.83,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:52.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha! Is Kureha the moon girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:58.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Does that make Ginko this forest girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:05.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Once upon a time, the worlds\Nwere divided in two by the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:07.56,Main,,0,0,0,,There was the moon world and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:09.98,Main,,0,0,0,,--...the forest world.\N--...the forest world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:14.69,Main,,0,0,0,,"You may not," said Kumaria,\N"for the two worlds are severed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:17.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Wanting to cross that severance is pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:20.28,Main,,0,0,0,,...a grave sin."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:24.53,Main,,0,0,0,,This is... my mother's love song?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:33.67,Main,,0,0,0,,"There is one way to make your wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:43.76,Main,,0,0,0,,If your love is true, your friend\Nwill be waiting for you on the other side."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:12.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Kumaria asked the two girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.21,0:22:18.63,Main,,0,0,0,,"Is your love the real thing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:21.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.84,0:22:28.72,Main,,0,0,0,,You're my friend, aren't you? You're "her."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:54.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the boundary that severed{\i0}\N{\i1}ripe moon from sleeping forest{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.79,0:23:01.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Break the law God shackles us with and smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.46,0:23:08.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I turned away from the bleating flock{\i0}\N{\i1}of shadows and howled my bloodthirsty ego{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.51,0:23:15.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here amidst the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.10,0:23:18.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Overflowing honey and soul{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.48,0:23:21.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to rend silk with my fangs{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:28.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm afraid you'll vanish{\i0}\N{\i1}like the world's last ray of hope{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.99,0:23:35.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The savage beast inside me{\i0}\N{\i1}tore out the throat of innocence{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:45.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on, shoot me through the heart{\i0}\N{\i1}with your sweet-scented Barrett of love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:02.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl-tee-hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.53,0:24:07.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, Lulu's Special\NHoney Ginger Milk is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.07,0:24:09.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.99,0:24:13.33,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.45,0:24:16.46,Main,,0,0,0,,"To the Criminal-Bear"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.71,0:24:18.21,Main,,0,0,0,,The criminal-bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.29,0:24:28.22,Main,,0,0,0,,"Ginko Yurishiro, I know the grave\Ncrime you committed. You are"--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.26,0:24:32.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko... This can't be!
